channel.title: I HATE linksys wireless router, can't get portforward to work
channel.description:
Well here is my problem, portforwarding like everyone else >.>...I'll explain what all I have and have done. I've gotten jdk6u2, compiler and restarter works fine. I have no-ip running and opened port through my firewall and called it purezscape.no-ip.biz. Using the port 43594 and turned my firewall off while trying to get people to log onto my server. I have a wireless WRT54G linkysy router and tried everything I could think of to fix it so people can log on. I failed at it, I have jdk recognized also. I have pictures of my portforward see if I did anything wrong...
[img]http://img170.imageshack.us/img170/7818/forwardei4.png[/img]
[img]http://img170.imageshack.us/img170/9926/forward2ja6.png[/img]
